msgid "Brewing Stand"
msgstr "양조기"

msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "인벤토리"

msgid "To use a brewing stand, rightclick it."
msgstr "양조기를 사용하려면 우클릭합니다."

msgid "To brew, you need blaze powder as fuel, a brewing material and at least 1 glass bottle filled with a liquid."
msgstr "양조하려면 연료로 블레이즈 가루와 양조 재료, 그리고 액체가 담긴 최소 1개의 유리병이 필요합니다."

msgid "Place the blaze powder in the left slot, the brewing material in the middle slot and 1-3 bottles in the remaining slots."
msgstr ""

msgid "When you have found a good combination, the brewing will commence automatically and steam starts to appear, using up the fuel and brewing material. The potions will soon be ready."
msgstr ""

msgid "Different combinations of brewing materials and liquids will give different results. Try to experiment!"
msgstr ""

msgid "Brew Potions"
msgstr ""

msgid "The stand allows you to brew potions!"
msgstr ""

